high_descs: Go to the stove to your left.
Take the pan from the stove.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Place the pan on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Take a few steps left to the stove.
Pick the pan up off the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pan on the bottom shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a few moments, then take it out again.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the pan on the front left burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a stove.

high_descs: Move across the room to the stove.
Pick up the black square pan that is on the stovetop.
Turn around and move toward the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pan inside.  Close the door and allow the pan to cool.  Open the fridge and pick up the pan.
Turn around and move back to the stove.
Place the pan on the right front burner.
anns.task_desc: Precool a pan for cooking purposes.
